00:00:43.990 --> 00:00:47.060
 solid, be strong, confidence on that.

00:00:47.060 --> 00:00:54.920
 Without the confidence, without this self-confidence and trusty, then the realization and

00:00:54.920 --> 00:00:56.560
 understanding will not come.

00:00:56.560 --> 00:01:01.360
 Even in samsara, without the confidence, we cannot really achieve so many things.

00:01:01.360 --> 00:01:06.840
 Without confidence means we are shaking, unshaking, we are not sure, we have stopped kind of

00:01:06.840 --> 00:01:07.640
 trembling.

00:01:07.640 --> 00:01:14.680
 That cannot succeed. So therefore, firmness, confidence is very, very important, and that is called

00:01:14.680 --> 00:01:15.920
 uncheckables.

