 It is not just a mundane status. So that purity is very good to remember everything, for example,

00:01:36.400 --> 00:01:44.020
 two arms, two legs, as well as one face, two arms, for example, as to truth, two legs, as to

00:01:44.020 --> 00:01:45.740
 different merits.

