00:03:42.900 --> 00:03:43.100
 Thelma,

00:03:43.100 --> 00:03:48.230
 teaching together with this great master, Pratugadha, and then this becomes one of the very

00:03:48.230 --> 00:03:50.360
 important practices in Numa schools.

